      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolute gem! This car is in pristine, mint condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously cared for, from the flawless exterior to the spotless interior, making it the perfect find for a discerning buyer who wants the very best.",
