    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in great shape for its next owner. It runs smoothly, looks wonderful, and is just waiting for someone to take it home. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways\u2014come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
